# ------------------------------- start overview ------------------------------- # 
    ==> Quick view: web socket is a new protocol to meet real time web application needs.

    ==> web socket features:
        - connection established by upgarding an existing HTTP connection to webSocket.
        - supported by browsers
            - ws://
            - wss://
        - HTTP standard prots 80,443.
            - this means: no firewall issues for the users.
        - full-duplex
            - the protocol allows communication in both directions.

    ==> connect to webSocket server.
    ==> Recieve notification about the opened connection use the onopen event lisnter.  
# ------------------------------- start overview ------------------------------- # 